title: Gary Moore - Still Got The Blues
description:
An Evening Of The Blues - Live Hammersmith Odeon 1990 (London, UK)

Duration: 01:12:12

Bitrate: 192kbps

Dimensions: 576x432

This is interspersed with comments from various musicians.
The comments appear to be subtitled in Japanese.   Needless
to say, Gary is not singing in Japanese.   The obvious conclusion
therefore is that this is a released in Japan copy.
